tone": null, "comments": 3, "created_at": "2017-09-19T01:10:24Z", "updated_at": "2017-09-20T03:09:54Z", "closed_at": "2017-09-20T01:34:09Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tensorflow/tensorflow/pulls/13140", "html_url": "https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/13140", "diff_url": "https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/13140.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/13140.patch"}, "body_html": "<p>Following the plan I mentioned in <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"250924691\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/12361\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/12361/hovercard?comment_id=323101744&amp;comment_type=issue_comment\" href=\"https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/12361#issuecomment-323101744\">#12361 (comment)</a>, I have refactored out the sync wrapper around copy between CPU and GPU.</p>\n<p>Now the user need to supply a <code>StatusCallback</code> when calling <code>RemoteMemoryManager:: TransportOptionsFromTensor </code> and <code>RemoteMemoryManager::TensorFromTransportOptions</code>, in order to prepare for the potential CPU-GPU tensor transfer.</p>", "body_text": "Following the plan I mentioned in #12361 (comment), I have refactored out the sync wrapper around copy between CPU and GPU.\nNow the user need to supply a StatusCallback when calling RemoteMemoryManager:: TransportOptionsFromTensor  and RemoteMemoryManager::TensorFromTransportOptions, in order to prepare for the potential CPU-GPU tensor transfer.", "body": "Following the plan I mentioned in https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/12361#issuecomment-323101744, I have refactored out the sync wrapper around copy between CPU and GPU.\r\n\r\nNow the user need to supply a `StatusCallback` when calling `RemoteMemoryManager:: TransportOptionsFromTensor ` and `RemoteMemoryManager::TensorFromTransportOptions`, in order to prepare for the potential CPU-GPU tensor transfer."}